Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:35.52,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}願伴君左右
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.69,0:23:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.57,0:23:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.61,0:23:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.53,0:23:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是指那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人和女人間做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.66,0:23:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是  反正都是學習啊  買東西啊這類事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.16,0:23:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早知道是這種笑點了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.58,0:23:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.75,0:24:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  啊  哎？
